Description: This field is used to record the material of which the documented physical object consists.
This field is used to record the technique used in the production of the documented object.
This field is used to record the type of measurement that the dimension of the documented object represents.
This field is used to record the value of the measured dimension of the documented object.
This field is used to record the unit of the measured dimension of the documented object.
This field is used to record the actor who undertook the measurement producing the dimension of the documented object.
